                <mxCell id="wf-note" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&#39;font-size: 17px;&#39;&gt;Compliance Monitoring — Key Steps Summary&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;1a-1d. Setup &amp;amp; Planning:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Monitoring Coordinator/Champion sets up ICRM EC context, reviews CRA/Publications/Consumer Complaints, develops Coverage Plan, locks and baselines Plans.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;2. Scoping:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Procedure Preparer defines Procedure Scope (AEs, GRC Risks, DSMT Segment, Geography). Approved by Procedure Reviewer (Maker-Checker).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;3. Planning:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Define ownership &amp;amp; execution timeline; Coverage Reports. Approved by Procedure Reviewer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;4. Design:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Create Procedure Steps, link GRC Activity, add Business Controls. Approved by Procedure Reviewer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;5. Execution:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Execute as designed; document outcomes; Validator uploads documentation. Review Manager sign-off captured in CRC.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;6. Exceptions (if any):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Raise exceptions; tag GRC risks, publications &amp;amp; policies. Gateway: Issue Required?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;7. CMIR:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Create CMIR in CRC; Document Approval from Business; create Issues/CAPs in iCAPS; publish CMIR. SLA: 7 calendar days from Execution End Date.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;CMIR Outside Monitoring:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Expedited Issue Report WITHOUT the full Plan/Design/Execution lifecycle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-10" y="1410" width="800" height="330" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="actor-note" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 17px;&quot;&gt;Actors &amp;amp; Roles&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Monitoring Coordinator:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; Creates/approves routines across ICRM ECs; can lock and baseline Plans.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Monitoring Champion:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; Same as Coordinator except CANNOT baseline Plans.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Procedure Preparer:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; Creates procedures (plans, designs, executions) for entitled ICRM ECs and MUs; &lt;br&gt;Assigned as First Delegate and Other Delegates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Procedure Reviewer / Review Manager:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; Approves routine plan, design and execution; sign-off captured in CRC.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Validator:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; Uploads documentation post execution (Read-Write role).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Monitoring Auditor:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; View-only access to completed executions and approved plans; &lt;br&gt;Takes precedence over all other CM roles when assigned.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Monitoring Admin:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; Can access all reports and add/modify MUs (Read-Only).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Monitoring QA:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; Read-Only access to all Procedures and Reports for all ICRM ECs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Procedure Viewer:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; View-only access to Plan and Design section.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt;Business / Issue Owner:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13px;&quot;&gt; Receives CMIR; provides Document Approval; designated as Issue Owner for remediation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#EBF5FB;strokeColor=#2E86C1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="840" y="1410" width="700" height="310" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
